[
    {
        "text": "Hi, everybody, and welcome.",
        "start": 0.539,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "In this video, we’re going to talk about\n‘this’ and ‘that’.",
        "start": 2.669,
        "duration": 4.971
    },
    {
        "text": "Now ‘this’ and ‘that’ are used to\ntalk about nouns",
        "start": 7.64,
        "duration": 4.86
    },
    {
        "text": "that are close to us, near or far away.",
        "start": 12.5,
        "duration": 4.86
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 17.36,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So let’s look at the board.",
        "start": 18.36,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is a flower.”",
        "start": 20.48,
        "duration": 2.541
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, we use ‘this’ to talk about one\nnoun, “a flower”, that is close.",
        "start": 23.021,
        "duration": 8.718
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 31.739,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is a flower.”",
        "start": 32.739,
        "duration": 2.221
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s not far.",
        "start": 34.96,
        "duration": 1.57
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s close.",
        "start": 36.53,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "“That is a flower.”",
        "start": 38.61,
        "duration": 2.05
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, we use ‘that’ to talk about one\nnoun that’s far away.",
        "start": 40.66,
        "duration": 7.29
    },
    {
        "text": "So, “That… that is a flower”.",
        "start": 47.95,
        "duration": 5.129
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 53.079,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "For another example…",
        "start": 54.079,
        "duration": 1.831
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is a marker.”",
        "start": 55.91,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s close to me.",
        "start": 58.31,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "But “That… that is a marker”.",
        "start": 60.95,
        "duration": 4.13
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s far away.",
        "start": 65.08,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, let’s move on to the next part.",
        "start": 67.18,
        "duration": 4.03
    },
    {
        "text": "So we know…",
        "start": 71.21,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is a flower.”",
        "start": 72.33,
        "duration": 1.951
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 74.281,
        "duration": 2.299
    },
    {
        "text": "And “That is a flower... that”.",
        "start": 76.58,
        "duration": 3.57
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, “Is this a flower”?",
        "start": 80.15,
        "duration": 2.99
    },
    {
        "text": "“What is it?”",
        "start": 83.14,
        "duration": 1.589
    },
    {
        "text": "“It’s a chair.”",
        "start": 84.729,
        "duration": 1.601
    },
    {
        "text": "So we have to use the negative.",
        "start": 86.33,
        "duration": 1.99
    },
    {
        "text": "“This isn’t a flower.”",
        "start": 88.32,
        "duration": 2.541
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s close by, but it isn’t a flower.",
        "start": 90.861,
        "duration": 4.548
    },
    {
        "text": "‘isn’t’ is a contraction for ‘is not’.",
        "start": 95.409,
        "duration": 4.511
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 99.92,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "“This isn’t a flower.”",
        "start": 100.92,
        "duration": 1.731
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is a chair.”",
        "start": 102.651,
        "duration": 1.979
    },
    {
        "text": "“That isn’t a flower.”",
        "start": 104.63,
        "duration": 3.83
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s far away, so we say “that”.",
        "start": 108.46,
        "duration": 3.13
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, we have ‘isn’t’, ‘a flower’.",
        "start": 111.59,
        "duration": 3.639
    },
    {
        "text": "“That’s a chair.”",
        "start": 115.229,
        "duration": 2.941
    },
    {
        "text": "And let’s take another example.",
        "start": 118.17,
        "duration": 1.67
    },
    {
        "text": "“This isn’t a pencil.”",
        "start": 119.84,
        "duration": 2.639
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is a marker.”",
        "start": 122.479,
        "duration": 2.621
    },
    {
        "text": "And…",
        "start": 125.1,
        "duration": 1.059
    },
    {
        "text": "“That isn’t a pencil.”",
        "start": 126.159,
        "duration": 3.03
    },
    {
        "text": "“That is a marker.”",
        "start": 129.189,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, let’s move on to the next part.",
        "start": 131.389,
        "duration": 3.35
    },
    {
        "text": "Now we’re going to learn how to use\n‘this’ and ‘that’ in a question.",
        "start": 134.739,
        "duration": 6.47
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 141.209,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So we know, “This is a flower”.",
        "start": 142.209,
        "duration": 3.661
    },
    {
        "text": "When we make a question, we have to switch.",
        "start": 145.87,
        "duration": 3.25
    },
    {
        "text": "We put the ‘be’ verb first.",
        "start": 149.12,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "So it becomes, “Is this a flower?”.",
        "start": 150.89,
        "duration": 4.329
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, it’s close by.",
        "start": 155.219,
        "duration": 2.35
    },
    {
        "text": "So the answer is, “Yes, it is”.",
        "start": 157.569,
        "duration": 3.741
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 161.31,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "“Is that a flower?”",
        "start": 162.31,
        "duration": 2.859
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s far away.",
        "start": 165.169,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "The answer is, “Yes, it is”.",
        "start": 167.269,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, but how about this?",
        "start": 170.269,
        "duration": 2.94
    },
    {
        "text": "“This isn’t a flower.”",
        "start": 173.209,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "So...",
        "start": 175.549,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "“Is this a flower?”.",
        "start": 176.549,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "The answer is, “No, it isn’t”.",
        "start": 179.269,
        "duration": 3.661
    },
    {
        "text": "“Is that a flower?”",
