        "duration": 2.669
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, here.",
        "start": 190.109,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "“Is this a marker?”.",
        "start": 191.389,
        "duration": 1.78
    },
    {
        "text": "“Yes, it is.”",
        "start": 193.169,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "“Is that a marker?”.",
        "start": 194.169,
        "duration": 3.171
    },
    {
        "text": "“Yes, it is.”",
        "start": 197.34,
        "duration": 3.609
    },
    {
        "text": "“Is this a pencil?”.",
        "start": 200.949,
