    {
        "text": "Hi, everybody and welcome to this video.",
        "start": 223.28,
        "duration": 3.179
    },
    {
        "text": "We’re going to talk about how to use ‘these’\nand ‘those’.",
        "start": 226.459,
        "duration": 4.92
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 231.379,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Uhhh, just like we learned with ‘this’\nand ‘that’,",
        "start": 232.379,
        "duration": 4.95
    },
    {
        "text": "we use ‘these’ and ‘those’ to talk\nabout nouns that are close to us",
        "start": 237.329,
        "duration": 6.38
    },
    {
        "text": "or far from us.",
        "start": 243.709,
        "duration": 1.87
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 245.579,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, let’s take a look at the board.",
        "start": 246.579,
        "duration": 3.13
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, we know if there is just one,",
        "start": 249.709,
        "duration": 3.581
    },
    {
        "text": "and it’s close to us,",
        "start": 253.29,
        "duration": 1.679
    },
    {
        "text": "we say, “This is a flower”.",
        "start": 254.969,
        "duration": 2.991
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 257.96,
        "duration": 1.23
    },
    {
        "text": "But there’s more than one.",
        "start": 259.19,
        "duration": 1.91
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s plural.",
        "start": 261.1,
        "duration": 1.37
    },
    {
        "text": "So we have to say, “These”.",
        "start": 262.47,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "“These are flowers.”",
        "start": 265.2,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, more than one.",
        "start": 267.52,
        "duration": 2.86
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, I change the ‘be’ verb to ‘are’",
        "start": 270.38,
        "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
        "text": "and I added an ‘s’ at the end of ‘flower’.",
        "start": 275.1,
        "duration": 3.67
    },
    {
        "text": "So, “These are flowers.”",
        "start": 278.77,
        "duration": 3.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 282.07,
        "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, there’s one that’s far away.",
        "start": 283.15,
        "duration": 3.62
    },
    {
        "text": "We say, “That is a flower.”",
        "start": 286.77,
        "duration": 3.321
    },
    {
        "text": "But, again, there’s more than one.",
        "start": 290.091,
        "duration": 3.229
    },
    {
        "text": "There are two flowers.",
        "start": 293.32,
        "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
        "text": "So, in that case, we use, “Those are flowers.”",
        "start": 294.97,
        "duration": 4.5
    },
    {
        "text": "“Those are flowers.”",
        "start": 299.47,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "They’re far away.",
        "start": 302.2,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "“Those are flowers.”",
        "start": 304.53,
        "duration": 1.67
    },
    {
        "text": "Let’s look at these.",
        "start": 306.2,
        "duration": 2.7
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is a marker.”",
        "start": 308.9,
        "duration": 2.23
    },
    {
        "text": "“These are markers.”",
        "start": 311.13,
        "duration": 3.65
    },
    {
        "text": "“That is a marker.”",
        "start": 314.78,
        "duration": 4.12
    },
    {
        "text": "“Those are markers.”",
        "start": 318.9,
        "duration": 4.39
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 323.29,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Let’s move on to the next part.",
        "start": 324.29,
        "duration": 3.19
    },
    {
        "text": "So we know “These are flowers”.",
        "start": 327.48,
        "duration": 3.22
    },
    {
        "text": "They’re close by.",
        "start": 330.7,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "And for the flowers that are far away, we\nsay,",
        "start": 333.16,
        "duration": 2.92
    },
    {
        "text": "“Those are flowers”.",
        "start": 336.08,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 339.12,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "But over here we have ‘chairs’.",
        "start": 340.14,
        "duration": 3.33
    },
    {
        "text": "So, we have to use the negative.",
        "start": 343.47,
        "duration": 2.71
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 346.18,
        "duration": 1.03
    },
    {
        "text": "We use the contraction ‘aren’t’",
        "start": 347.21,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "which is short for ‘are not’.",
        "start": 350.33,
        "duration": 3.22
    },
    {
        "text": "“These aren’t flowers.”",
        "start": 353.55,
        "duration": 3.47
    },
    {
        "text": "“These aren’t flowers.",
        "start": 357.02,
        "duration": 3.48
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, and for the chairs that are far away,",
        "start": 360.5,
        "duration": 2.68
    },
    {
        "text": "we say, “Those aren’t flowers”.",
        "start": 363.18,
        "duration": 4.28
    },
    {
        "text": "“Those aren’t flowers.”",
        "start": 367.46,
        "duration": 3.21
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, and let’s try with the markers.",
        "start": 370.67,
        "duration": 3.26
    },
    {
        "text": "“These aren’t pens.”",
        "start": 373.93,
        "duration": 3.31
    },
    {
        "text": "“These aren’t pens.”",
        "start": 377.24,
        "duration": 3.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, and far away.",
        "start": 380.54,
        "duration": 2.71
    },
    {
        "text": "“Those aren’t pens.”",
        "start": 383.25,
        "duration": 2.42
    },
    {
        "text": "“Those aren’t pens.”",
        "start": 385.67,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, let’s move on to the next part.",
        "start": 388.1,
        "duration": 3.05
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, now we’re going to make some questions.",
        "start": 391.15,
        "duration": 4.74
    },
    {
        "text": "We know, “These are flowers”.",
        "start": 395.89,
        "duration": 3.88
    },
    {
        "text": "When you want to make a question, you have\nto change",
        "start": 399.77,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "‘these are’ and put the ‘be’ verb\nfirst.",
        "start": 402.65,
        "duration": 3.63
    },
    {
        "text": "So, it becomes, “Are these flowers?”.",
        "start": 406.28,
        "duration": 4.41
    },
    {
        "text": "“Are these flowers?”",
        "start": 410.69,
        "duration": 2.51
    },
    {
        "text": "And the answer is “Yes, they are.”",
        "start": 413.2,
        "duration": 3.38
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, now the flowers are far away.",
        "start": 416.58,
        "duration": 3.13
    },
    {
        "text": "So we say, “Are those flowers?”.",
        "start": 419.71,
        "duration": 2.66
    },
    {
        "text": "“Are those flowers?”",
        "start": 422.37,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "And again, the answer is “Yes, they are.”",
        "start": 425.25,
        "duration": 3.9
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 429.15,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Now here, we have chairs.",
        "start": 430.15,
        "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
        "text": "“Are these flowers?”",
        "start": 432.17,
        "duration": 3.41
    },
    {
        "text": "The answer is “No, they aren’t.”",
        "start": 435.58,
        "duration": 3.98
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, now they’re far away.",
        "start": 439.56,
        "duration": 3.23
    },
    {
        "text": "“Are those flowers?”",
        "start": 442.79,
        "duration": 2.61
    },
    {
        "text": "And again, the answer is “No, they aren’t.”",
        "start": 445.4,
        "duration": 4.41
    },
    {
        "text": "How about these?",
        "start": 449.81,
        "duration": 1.07
    },
    {
        "text": "“Are these markers?”",
        "start": 450.88,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": "“Yes, they are.”",
        "start": 452.86,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "“Are those markers?”",
        "start": 455.74,
        "duration": 2.49
    },
    {
        "text": "“Yes, they are.”",
        "start": 458.23,
        "duration": 3.39
    },
    {
        "text": "“Are these pens?”",
        "start": 461.62,
        "duration": 2.7
    },
    {
        "text": "“No, they aren’t.”",
        "start": 464.32,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "“Are those pens?”",
        "start": 466.62,
        "duration": 3.049
    },
    {
        "text": "“No, they aren’t.”",
        "start": 469.669,
        "duration": 3.061
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, so in this video, we learned how to\nuse ‘these’ and ‘those’.",
        "start": 472.73,
        "duration": 5.55
    },
    {
        "text": "I hope you guys understand and I’ll see\nyou in the next video.",
        "start": 478.28,
        "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Bye.",
        "start": 482.04,
        "duration": 1.05
    },
    {
        "text": "Let’s do some practice with\n‘this’, ‘that’, ‘these’, and ‘those’.",
        "start": 483.09,
        "duration": 5.9
    },
    {
        "text": "First, I have this pen.",
        "start": 488.99,
        "duration": 3.49
    },
    {
        "text": "I have to say, “This is a pen.”",
        "start": 492.48,
        "duration": 2.939
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is a pen.”",
        "start": 495.419,
        "duration": 2.561
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 497.98,
        "duration": 2.61
    },
    {
        "text": "Over there, “That is a pen.”",
        "start": 500.59,
        "duration": 2.53
    },
    {
        "text": "“That is a pen.”",
        "start": 503.12,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, I have two pens.",
        "start": 505.46,
        "duration": 4.86
    },
    {
        "text": "“These are pens.”",
        "start": 510.32,
        "duration": 1.909
    },
    {
        "text": "“These are pens.”",
        "start": 512.229,
        "duration": 2.69
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, I’m going to move them far away.",
        "start": 514.919,
        "duration": 3.761
    },
    {
        "text": "“Those are pens.”",
        "start": 518.68,
        "duration": 1.989
    },
    {
        "text": "“Those are pens.”",
        "start": 520.669,
        "duration": 2.59
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, let’s move on to questions.",
        "start": 523.259,
        "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
        "text": "I have one pen.",
        "start": 527.019,
        "duration": 2.721
    },
    {
        "text": "“Is this a pen?”",
        "start": 529.74,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": "“Yes, it is.”",
        "start": 532.26,
        "duration": 2.699
    },
    {
        "text": "“Is this a cookie?”",
        "start": 534.959,
        "duration": 3.591
    },
    {
        "text": "“No, it isn’t.”",
        "start": 538.55,
        "duration": 2.69
    },
    {
        "text": "“Is that a pen?”",
        "start": 541.24,
        "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
        "text": "“Yes, it is.”",
        "start": 542.8,
        "duration": 1.789
    },
    {
        "text": "“Is that a cookie?”",
        "start": 544.589,
        "duration": 5.881
    },
    {
        "text": "“No, it isn’t.”",
        "start": 550.47,
        "duration": 2.419
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, two pens.",
        "start": 552.889,
        "duration": 2.05
    },
    {
        "text": "“Are these pens?”",
        "start": 554.939,
        "duration": 2.051
